ZH: 我们的毛巾里含有棉花。
EN: Our towels are made with cotton.

ZH: 棉花是一种天然的纤维。
EN: Cotton is a natural fiber.

ZH: 这件衬衫的质地非常柔软，因为它是用棉花制成的。
EN: The texture of this shirt is very soft because it is made of cotton.

ZH: 棉花是南方非常重要的农业作物。
EN: Cotton is a very important agricultural crop in the south.

ZH: 这种被子里包含了棉花和羽毛。
EN: This comforter contains both cotton and feathers.

ZH: 你可以用棉花来填充这个抱枕。
EN: You can use cotton to stuff this pillow.

ZH: 棉花在古代是非常珍贵的贸易商品。
EN: Cotton was a very valuable commodity in ancient times.

ZH: 我们应该减少使用化学材料，多用棉花这种天然材料。
EN: We should reduce the use of chemicals and use more natural materials like cotton.

ZH: 棉花生长在温暖的气候中。
EN: Cotton grows in warm climates.

ZH: 这款裙子非常透气，因为它是用纯棉花制成的。
EN: This dress is very breathable because it is made of pure cotton.

ZH: 巴西是棉花的主要生产国之一。
EN: Brazil is one of the major cotton-producing countries.

ZH: 棉花被广泛用于制作衣服和床上用品。
EN: Cotton is widely used in making clothes and bedding.

ZH: 他们用棉花填充了这只布娃娃。
EN: They stuffed this cloth doll with cotton.

ZH: 这家工厂每年生产数千吨棉花。
EN: This factory produces thousands of tons of cotton every year.

ZH: 棉花在全球纺织工业中扮演着重要的角色。
EN: Cotton plays an important role in the global textile industry.

ZH: 棉花的花朵非常漂亮，是一种草地上的美丽景观。
EN: Cotton flowers are very beautiful and create a lovely landscape in the fields.

ZH: 这种床单的棉花含量很高。
EN: The cotton content of this bedsheet is very high.

ZH: 棉花的收割季节通常在秋天。
EN: The harvesting season for cotton is usually in the fall.

ZH: 棉花在工业制造中有着重要的应用。
EN: Cotton has important applications in industrial manufacturing.

ZH: 这家公司专门从南非进口优质棉花。
EN: This company specializes in importing high-quality cotton from South Africa.
